structure.unit: COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS
GENERAL PROVISIONS APPLICABLE TO COUNTIES, CITIES, AND OTHER LOCAL UNITS

law.catch_line: KRS 65.680 to 65.699 limited to development areas established under KRS 65.686 by a city or county before March 23, 2007.
law.text:
Effective on March 23, 2007, the provisions of KRS 65.680 to 65.699 shall apply only to development areas which are:
Established under KRS 65.686 by a city or county prior to March 23, 2007; and
Subject to the provisions of a grant contract executed prior to March 23, 2007.
law.history: Created 2007 Ky. Acts ch. 95, sec. 24, effective March 23, 2007.
